erlang (1:21.1.1+dfsg-2) unstable; urgency=medium

  The epmd.socket and epmd.service units, which serve the Erlang portmapper
  daemon, are now enabled by default and the socket is listening on the
  loopback interface only. If you want to reconfigure or disable them,
  please consult README.Debian.
    
 -- Sergei Golovan <sgolovan@debian.org>  Wed, 17 Oct 2018 10:23:43 +0300
